###Angel (Balisse)
Brand of the Impenitent		KEY:Balisse ~ Brand of the Impenitent		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural					DESC:Three times per day, a balisse angel can brand a judged individual within 30 feet. The target must succeed at a DC %1 Will save or be branded with a painless, glowing icon on its chest-usually the holy symbol of the deity or empyreal lord the balisse angel serves. This brand lasts for %2 days. Anyone who attacks the branded target gains a +2 sacred bonus on weapon attack and damage rolls and a +2 sacred bonus on caster level checks to overcome the target's spell resistance.|15+CHA|TL

