Piercing Hymn			KEY:Choral Angel ~ Piercing Hymn			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural					DESC:As a standard action, a choral angel can launch a concentrated blast of sonic energy from its mouth. This attack has a range of 90 feet with no range increment. Any creature struck by a choral angel's piercing hymn must succeed at a DC %1 Fortitude save or be deafened for 1d4 minutes.|14+CHA

###Archon (Spyglass)
